- Large files: **[quiz.js](mdc:quiz.js)** (42KB), **[styles.css](mdc:styles.css)** (29KB)
- Optimize media files before adding to **[images/](mdc:images)** or **[audio/](mdc:audio)**
- Test responsive design on various screen sizes

